OL,3,CRugby league legend plans final MND
OL,4,Cchallenge
OL,6,FRugby league legend Kevin Sinfield has
OL,7,Fannounced his final challenge to raise
OL,8,Fmoney for motor neurone disease
OL,9,Fcharities.
OL,11,FThe event is inspired by his friend
OL,12,Fand former Leeds Rhinos teammate Rob
OL,13,FBurrow, who died in 2024 after living
OL,14,Fwith MND for four-and-a-half years.
OL,16,FIn his seventh challenge, 45-year-old
OL,17,FSinfield will run an ultra marathon
OL,18,Fevery day for seven days in September.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
