OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781118693
OL,3,CRugby league legend plans final MND
OL,4,Cchallenge
OL,6,FThe route will include all 12 Betfred
OL,7,FSuper League grounds on his way from
OL,8,FHull KR's Craven Park to Old Trafford
OL,9,Fin Manchester. The final endurance
OL,10,Ftest will see him arrive onto the
OL,11,Fpitch in time for the Super League
OL,12,FGrand Final on Saturday 3 October.
OL,14,FOn what will be his final challenge,
OL,15,FSinfield will visit the following
OL,16,Fgrounds and locations on his route:
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781118693
OL,3,CRugby league legend plans final MND
OL,4,Cchallenge
OL,6,FEach day will be separated into 7km
OL,7,Fblocks to be completed within an hour
OL,8,Falongside an 'Extra Mile' event,
OL,9,Frunning alongside those affected by
OL,10,FMND each day.
OL,12,FSince the first challenge in 2020,
OL,13,FSinfield and the team have raised more
OL,14,Fthan #11m for the MND community.
OL,16,FThis year will be even more poignant
OL,17,Ffor the Burrow family due to the
OL,18,Fpassing of Rob's father Geoff in March
OL,19,Ffollowing a period of ill health.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
