PN,36904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1781118693
OL,3,CRugby league legend plans final MND
OL,4,Cchallenge
OL,6,FOn his fundraising efforts so far,
OL,7,FSinfield told BBC Breakfast: "Our team
OL,8,Fhave done a wonderful job. I couldn't
OL,9,Fhave done any of it without them, they
OL,10,Fare so unselfish in the way they've
OL,11,Fgone about this.
OL,13,F"We couldn't have done this on our
OL,14,Fown. The money has gone a long way and
OL,15,Fwe're getting closer and closer but
OL,16,Fwe've got to keep pushing, we've got
OL,17,Fto try and find a cure."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
